oai_dc:dc.dc:title: OXIDATIVE STUDIES ON TRANS-(3-PHENYL-2-PROPENYL)PHENOLS AND 2-METHOXY-4-(2-PROPENYL)PHENOL AND 2-METHOXY-4-(1-PROPENYL)PHENOL
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: IYER, MR
BASKARAN, S
TRIVEDI, GK
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Oxidative reaction on trans-2-(3-phenyl-2-propenyl)phenols (1-4) and para-alkenylphenols have been studied. The products formed include benzofurane (5-8) and neolignane (16-18).
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: JOURNAL OF THE INDIAN CHEMICAL SOCIETY, 71(6-8), 341-343
